G'day <%= @user.first_name %>,

  Congratulations, your offer was accepted!

  Your new patrol
  ---------------
  <%= @request.roster.patrol.name %>
  <%= @request.roster.start.strftime("%A %d %B %Y") %>
  <%= @request.roster.start.strftime("%H:%M") %> - <%= @request.roster.finish.strftime("%H:%M") %>

  You are now a sub for <%= @request.user.name %>.

  Your old patrol
  ---------------
  <%= @offer.roster.patrol.name %>
  <%= @offer.roster.start.strftime("%A %d %B %Y") %>
  <%= @offer.roster.start.strftime("%H:%M") %> - <%= @offer.roster.finish.strftime("%H:%M") %>

  <%= @request.user.name %> is now a sub for you.

  <% if @request.email.present? || @request.mobile.present? %>
  Need to get in contact?
  -----------------------
  You can contact <%= @request.user.name %> via the details below.
  <%= @request.email %>
  <%= @request.mobile %>
  <% end %>

  Can't make your new patrol?
  ---------------------------
  You are now responsible for turning up to your new patrol. If you can't make it, you will need to swap it again. You cannot cancel a swap once it has been confirmed (but you can swap back).


  See your updated roster at Swapsea at <%= dashboard_url %>

  Have a great weekend!

  Much Love,
  Swapsea
